  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. A mesh-independence verification activity is declared and described in detail; however, the evidence artifacts generated by that activity are inadvertently linked to the grid-convergence study activity rather than to the mesh-independence activity, leaving the declared verification activity without any evidence provenance link.",
