      "rationale": "A grid-convergence study was performed and GCI values reported for velocity fields. GCI for hemolysis index on the medium mesh is 3.2%, satisfying the threshold. However, apparent order of convergence for the hemolysis transport scalar was not separately reported. Achieved level 3 against required level 4."
    },
    {
