      "rationale": "FDA benchmark experiments used porcine blood at 37°C; COU specifies human blood at physiological hematocrit range. Fluid property differences are documented but not corrected for. Temperature control uncertainty in experiments was ±2°C. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
    },
